data.description: Gorgeous 3/2 located in east Boynton with access to parks, boat ramps, I-95, shopping, mall, shopping and restaurants. Home has impact windows throughout, newer A/C and water heater, custom bathrooms and a huge yard which the owner takes plenty of pride in. Yard has an array of fruit and nut trees including: Guava, plantain, avocado, banana, coconut, soursop, island spinach, mango, mint, almond, as well as even sweet potato. Come and tour this tropical paradise now!
